2 pounds ground beef
2 boxes of ziti noodles
3 jars of sauce
1 package of cream cheese
1 large container of ricotta cheese
2 blocks of mozzarella
8 ounces of Parmesan

Brown the ground beef, boil the noodles, mix the noodles, beef, sauce, cream cheese, ricotta, and half the mozzarella and Parmesan

baked at 350 for 1.5 hours covered, then put the rest of the cheese on top and bake for another 30 minutes

